aunt karen im gonna miss u so much. u were to young and u went through to much in ur life to have this happen to u, u did not deserve this at all. all i can try to think about is the times when u lived here and we would have so much fun. we would walk annie every night together and just have so much fun. it used to be so good to be able to talk to u. and if i couldnt sleep i new i could always come down the basement and find u and u would talk to me and let me stay up late with u and watch leno and the news. oh the good times. i miss u and annie not living here we all used to have a good time. then when u moved out we would come over to ur new apartment and visit and i would spend the night and have alot of fun. then we had our dinners at friendlys with me u and mom. i always gonna miss all of that but i will always remember all of those times and u will always be in my heart. u r one of the closest people i have ever lost in my life and i still dont believe it happening i thought that it was all a joke when my mom called me yesterday and told me what happened and i started screaming and crying. it was horrible and my friends came over and tried to comfort me and be there for me. thanx to all of u ur the best. i dont understand y it was u, u were goin to get surgery soon and everything was supposed to be all better. y did this happen u did not deserve this at all u to young to die and it just doesnt seem true. tom is goin to be really hard for everyone along with saturday but we will get through it just promise u will always be there with us. aunt karen i luv u and i miss u so much. thank you for all the good times we have been through and always being there for me. u will be missed by many people. i luv u!
                                <3 always ~ stacey

Your soul is bound to the Rose Petals: The
Wronged. "'ve come undone and all hopes of mending
me are gone because the pain took my soul.
Can't you see? The only one who can put me
back together again is me." The Rose Petals are associated with sorrow,
reflection, and wisdom. They are governed by
the goddess Persephone and their sign is The
Teardrop, or Broken Love. As a Rose Petal, you are always self-reflective and
may be hard on yourself. You probably have
been hurt in the past by other people and can
sometimes distance yourself, as a result. You
don't usually let other get too close to you,
but you are very good at mending your spirits
back together by yourself.

What Rose Is Your Soul Bound To?
